{"tid":270102,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（一帶一路）肯尼亞蒙內鐵路通車　華派特使出席啟用儀式","createTime":"2017-06-04T06:16:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T17:48:00.000Z","uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c106203d8acf0e7b74b7500ecfd487d312559b9a","tid":270102,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:16:12.000Z","msg":"由中國承建、連接肯尼亞蒙巴薩及內羅畢地區的蒙內鐵路今日正式通車，作為中方特使的國務委員王勇，與肯尼亞總統尤休留肯亞塔共同出席通車儀式。內地傳媒報道，尤休留肯亞塔會親自登車試乘，成為蒙內鐵路的首位乘客。<br />\n<br />\n另外，中國路橋工程有限責任公司昨日與肯尼亞鐵路公司，在蒙巴薩簽署10年的運營及維護合同。合同採用「5＋5」的方式，規定中方負責蒙內鐵路的車輛調度安排、鐵路及機車的維護保養等工作，同時為肯方提供技術轉移、人員培訓等服務；而肯方將在第5年對中方的服務進行績效評估。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，蒙內鐵路全長480公里，於2014年12月動工，採用中國國鐵一級標準設計施工，除了是肯尼亞獨立百年來建成的首條鐵路，亦是首條海外的「全中國標準鐵路」。鐵路開通後，將來還會再接通烏干達、盧旺達、南蘇丹等東非5個國家。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170531/photo/bkncn-20170531143546336-0531_05011_001_01b.jpg?20170531155020\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170531%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170531143546336-0531_05011_001_01b.jpg%3F20170531155020&h=57195290&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IaFil6h0sM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D3IaFil6h0sM&d=vBAjQ5xdjjLSHqkih4VZf0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=c914dd4c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3IaFil6h0sM</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=axkeiGIRNuM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaxkeiGIRNuM&d=vBAjQ5xdjjLSHqkih4VZf0bWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=fe841623\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=axkeiGIRNuM</a>"},{"pid":"2138852c47187ac565789144f0280f47ceb23fb0","tid":270102,"uid":93839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T06:19:52.000Z","msg":"同當年英國法國爭住打通南北不謀而合"},{"pid":"6e3dfc8fbf52ee51c0106ef6fedd3e26e15a103e","tid":270102,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:23:17.000Z","msg":"憤青駁唔到?"},{"pid":"c100b7a399010d33d091f7fb3be907f08eb86199","tid":270102,"uid":43712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T08:25:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/269923/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/269923/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"4f4540c3be4394d35de3aa21e65ff530dcc36065","tid":270102,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:48:00.000Z","msg":"樂觀SIR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}